            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="18616814">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">图考相册：http://www.douban.com/photos/album/72352715/


图11 Dioscoride manuscript 这个好喜欢但是找不到资料啊！

图12 Benedetti Rinio 写的草药书 herbal 1419 (Italian herbalist who compiled one of the most well-known herbal encyclopedias of the era. Rinio's Liber de simplicibus, published in Venice in 1410, contained 440 illustrations by Venetianartist Andrea Amadio. The book discussed 450 do...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-05-31 11:54</span>
                  
